Title: The Sixth Extinction (2)
Plot: While Scully travels to Africa to piece together the meaning of the symbols on the spaceship beached on the Ivory Coast, Mulder is imprisoned by his own frenetic brain activity. He manages to get a message to Skinner who finds Kritschgau, and together they try to understand what is happening to Mulder before it is too late.
GuestStars: Warren Sweeney, Mari Weiss, Abdoulaye N'Gom, Anthony Okungbowa, Michael Ensign, Jo Nell Kennedy, Conrad Roberts
